//
// High-performance lock-free concurrent data structures:
// - MPMC Queue (Michael-Scott queue)
// - MPMC Stack (Treiber stack)
// - Lock-free HashMap (split-ordered lists)
// - Work-stealing Deque (Chase-Lev)
